<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="js" lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta content="width=device-width" name="viewport">
    <title>Add claim: How have you been affected? | MyService</title>
    <link href="docs/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="uikit-body uikit-grid uikit-refactor">
    <noscript><p role="alert">This website needs JavaScript to work properly.</p></noscript>
    <nav class="uikit-skip-link"><a class="uikit-skip-link__link" href="#main-content">Skip to main content</a></nav>
    <% include ../../../global/partials/header-topbar.ejs %>
    <% include ../../../global/partials/header-claims.ejs %>
    <% include ../partials/help-button.ejs %>
    <main> 
    <div class="container" id="main-content">
    <div id="progressbar"><div id="percentage"></div></div>
    <h1>Permanent impairment compensation</h1>
    
    <div class="form-group">

  		<div class="tip--wrapper line-break-after">
    		<p class="text-fullwidth">If your claim for liability is accepted you may be entitled to <a href="https://www.dva.gov.au/factsheet-mrc07-permanent-impairment-compensation-payments" rel="external" target="_black">permanent&nbsp;impairment&nbsp;compensation</a> if:</p>
    		<ul style="margin-bottom:20px;">
    			<li>after treatment you still have an impairment or lifestyle rescriction,</li>
    			<li>the impairment or restriction is likely to continue indefinitely, and</li>
    			<li>your condition has stabilised.</li>
    		</ul>
    		<p class="text-fullwidth no-space-after">The application process invloves one or multiple medical assessments to determine the level of impairment or lifestyle restriction.</p>
    	</div>

		<fieldset>
			<legend class="legend-label">Would you like to apply for permanent impairment compensation?<span class="display-block hint">This is not your only chance. You can apply at any time after liability is accepted.</span></legend>
			<div class="radio-toggle">
				<label class="on label-left" for="pi-yes"><input id="pi-yes" type="radio" name="pi"><span>Yes</span></label>
				<label class="off label-right" for="pi-no"><input id="pi-no" type="radio" name="pi"><span>Not now</span></label>
			</div>
		  
			<div class="form-group pi-yes" style="display:none;">
				<p>If liability for your condition is accepted, we will get in touch with you about the next steps.</p>
			</div>
     
     		<div class="form-group pi-no" style="display:none;">
				<p>There will be other opportunities to apply for permanent impairment compensation if liability for your condition is accepted.</p>
			</div>
      
		</fieldset>
    
	</div>
  
    <div class="pagination">
        <button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary" onclick="window.location.href = '/claim4'">Previous</button>
        <button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary" onclick="window.location.href = '#open-modal'">Cancel</button>
        <div class="floated">
            <button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary" onclick="window.location.href = '/claim4'">Save and exit</button>&nbsp;
            <button class="uikit-btn btnNext" onclick="window.location.href = '/claim6'">Save and next</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <% include ../partials/cancel-modal.ejs %>
    </div>

  </main>
  
  <% include ../../../global/partials/footer.ejs %>
  <% include ../partials/panel-help.ejs %>

	<script>
	
	// Progress percentage
    document.getElementById("percentage").style.width = "85%";

	// PI messages
	$( "#pi-yes" ).click(function() {
      $( ".pi-no" ).hide();
	  $( ".pi-yes" ).show("fast");
    });
    $( "#pi-no" ).click(function() {
	  $( ".pi-yes" ).hide();
      $( ".pi-no" ).show("fast");
    });
	</script>

</body>
</html>